net.proteusframework.ui.miwt.util

Class ImageDisplayWrapper

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.proteusframework.ui.miwt.util.ImageDisplayWrapper
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    ButtonDisplayWrapper

    abstract class ImageDisplayWrapper
extends Object
    Helper class for ComponentDisplay subclasses that have Image objects that need to allocate resources.
    Author:
    Pat B. Double (double@i2rd.com)
